Invocation Name: fashion island
Developer Terms of Use
des: Fashion Island is here to help you find out more about shops and amenities at Fashion Island Shopping Center in Newport Beach. If you're in search of a store, a service or a bite to eat, you can now find it instantly by simply asking the Fashion Island Alexa Skill. Try it! Simply ask questions like, "Alexa, ask Fashion Island, where is Neiman Marcus located?" or " Alexa, ask Fashion Island, where I can valet?" or " Alexa, ask Fashion Island, where are the restrooms?" and our IBM Watson-enhanced guest services experience will help you shop and navigate Fashion Island instantly. Go ahead and try it out. We're always here and At Your Service.
